                <p>For example, we offer a comprehensive refrigerator maintenance service for a flat fee of $80. This service includes professional cleaning and inspection, helping to prevent damage and ensure your refrigerator operates efficiently for years to come.</p>
                <p>By following these maintenance tips and scheduling regular professional services, you can extend the life of your refrigerator, improve its efficiency, and avoid costly repairs.</p>
